description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Ezo Red Foxes that Get Along Well
-Ezo Squirrel
-Pika Rabbit
-A Mother and her Duckling
-Ezo Chipmunk
-Ezo Red Fox “Yawn”
-Ezo Squirrel “Crunchy!”
-Pika Rabbit 2
-Baby Ducklings
-Ezo Chipmunk 2
name: Fluffy Animals in Hokkaido / Kenta Igarashi
